Is the first full-lenght release band from Crakow. Band was founded in 2008. Before this album they released 1 of four-track's demo: "Okryte Zapomnieniem" in 2013.
They sing in Polish rare-folk dialect of Malopolska (land in Southern Poland), and in English. Title of this album in English means: "Between of East and West".
